? Use a separate <form> or <orth>?
  - Ask at Freedict first.

For different US/UK spellings (or similar):
 - ex. from TEI doc
     <form>
      <orth>colour</orth>
      <form>
       <usg type="geo">US</usg>
       <orth>color</orth>
      </form>
     </form>
    - https://www.tei-c.org/release/doc/tei-p5-doc/en/html/DI.html : 9.3.5.2
